show.description: Twin sisters separated in childhood reunite through love, betrayal, and revenge. When Disha's adopted family destroys her life and steals her designs, her twin Nisha takes on her identity to seek justice. A gripping tale of sisterhood, corporate intrigue, and second chances in Mumbai's fashion world. Watch Now!
